165 	/**
166 	 * Fix broken url.
167 	 *
168 	 * @param nextPage
169 	 *            the next page
170 	 * @return the string
171 	 */
172 	private static String fixBrokenUrl(final String nextPage) {
173 		if (nextPage.startsWith("//")) {
174 			return "http:" + nextPage;
175 		} else {
176 			return nextPage;
177 		}
178 	}
179 
180 	/**
181 	 * Process all.
182 	 *
183 	 * @param dokument
184 	 *            the dokument
185 	 * @param processStrategy
186 	 *            the process strategy
187 	 */
188 	private static void processAll(final List<DocumentElement> dokument,
189 			final ProcessDataStrategy<DocumentElement> processStrategy) {
190 		for (final DocumentElement documentElement : dokument) {
191 
192 			try {
193 				processStrategy.process(documentElement);
194 			} catch (final RuntimeException e) {
195 				LOGGER.warn(ERROR_PROCESSING_DOCUMENT, documentElement.getId(), e);
196 			}
197 		}
198 	}
199 
200 	/* (non-Javadoc)
201 	 * @see com.hack23.cia.service.external.riksdagen.api.RiksdagenDocumentApi#getDocumentContent(java.lang.String)
202 	 */
203 	@Override
204 	public DocumentContentData getDocumentContent(final String id) throws DataFailureException {
205 		try {
206 			return new DocumentContentData().withId(UrlHelper.urlEncode(id,StandardCharsets.UTF_8.toString()))
207 					.withContent(xmlAgent.retriveContent(DOCUMENT_CONTENT.replace(DOC_ID_KEY, id)));
208 		} catch (final XmlAgentException e) {
209 			LOGGER.warn(PROBLEM_GETTING_DOCUMENT_CONTENT_FOR_ID_S_FROM_DATA_RIKSDAGEN_SE, id);
210 			throw new DataFailureException(e);
211 		}
212 	}
213 
214 	/* (non-Javadoc)
215 	 * @see com.hack23.cia.service.external.riksdagen.api.RiksdagenDocumentApi#getDocumentList(com.hack23.cia.model.external.riksdagen.dokumentstatus.impl.DocumentType, int)
216 	 */
217 	@Override
218 	public List<DocumentElement> getDocumentList(final DocumentType documentType, final int maxNumberPages)
219 			throws DataFailureException {
220 		try {
221 			return loadDocumentList(DOCUMENT_LIST_TYPE.replace(TYPE_KEY, documentType.value()), maxNumberPages);
222 		} catch (final XmlAgentException e) {
223 			LOGGER.warn(PROBLEM_GETTING_DOCUMENT_LIST_FOR_DOCUMENT_TYPE_S_MAX_NUMBER_PAGES_S_FROM_DATA_RIKSDAGEN_SE,
224 					documentType, Integer.toString(maxNumberPages));
225 			throw new DataFailureException(e);
226 		}
227 	}

240 		}
241 	}

243 	/* (non-Javadoc)
244 	 * @see com.hack23.cia.service.external.riksdagen.api.RiksdagenDocumentApi#getDocumentList(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, int)
245 	 */
246 	@Override
247 	public List<DocumentElement> getDocumentList(final String changedSinceDate, final String changedToDate,
248 			final int maxNumberPages) throws DataFailureException {
249 		try {
250 			return loadDocumentList(DOCUMENT_LIST_CHANGED_DATE.replace(CHANGED_SINCE_KEY, changedSinceDate)
251 					.replace(CHANGED_TO_KEY, changedToDate), maxNumberPages);
252 		} catch (final XmlAgentException e) {
253 			LOGGER.warn(PROBLEM_GETTING_DOCUMENT_LIST_CHANGED_SINCE_DATE_S_CHANGED_TO_DATE_S_FROM_DATA_RIKSDAGEN_SE,
254 					changedSinceDate, changedToDate);
255 			throw new DataFailureException(e);
256 		}
257 	}

259 	/* (non-Javadoc)
260 	 * @see com.hack23.cia.service.external.riksdagen.api.RiksdagenDocumentApi#getDocumentStatus(java.lang.String)
261 	 */
262 	@Override
263 	public DocumentStatusContainer getDocumentStatus(final String id) throws DataFailureException {
264 		try {
265 			final String url = DOCUMENT_STATUS.replace(ID_KEY, UrlHelper.urlEncode(id,StandardCharsets.UTF_8.toString()));
266 			return ((JAXBElement<DocumentStatusContainer>) xmlAgent.unmarshallXml(riksdagenDocumentStatusMarshaller,
267 					url, HTTP_DOKUMENTSTATUS_RIKSDAGEN_EXTERNAL_MODEL_CIA_HACK23_COM_IMPL, null, null)).getValue();
268 		} catch (final XmlAgentException e) {
269 			LOGGER.warn(PROBLEM_GETTING_DOCUMENT_STATUS_ID_S_FROM_DATA_RIKSDAGEN_SE, id);
270 			throw new DataFailureException(e);
271 		} 
272 	}

275 	/**
276 	 * Load and process document list.
277 	 *
278 	 * @param url
279 	 *            the url
280 	 * @param processStrategy
281 	 *            the process strategy
282 	 * @throws XmlAgentException
283 	 *             the xml agent exception
284 	 */
285 	private void loadAndProcessDocumentList(final String url,
286 			final ProcessDataStrategy<DocumentElement> processStrategy) throws XmlAgentException {
287 		final DocumentContainerElement dokumentLista = ((JAXBElement<DocumentContainerElement>) xmlAgent.unmarshallXml(
288 				riksdagenDocumentListMarshaller, url, HTTP_DOKUMENTLISTA_RIKSDAGEN_EXTERNAL_MODEL_CIA_HACK23_COM_IMPL,
289 				null, null)).getValue();
290 
291 		int resultSize = dokumentLista.getDokument().size();
292 		processAll(dokumentLista.getDokument(), processStrategy);
293 		final BigInteger pages = dokumentLista.getTotalPages();
294 		for (int i = 1; i < pages.intValue(); i++) {
295 			final DocumentContainerElement otherPagesdokumentLista = ((JAXBElement<DocumentContainerElement>) xmlAgent
296 					.unmarshallXml(riksdagenDocumentListMarshaller, url + PAGE_PROPERTY + i,
297 							HTTP_DOKUMENTLISTA_RIKSDAGEN_EXTERNAL_MODEL_CIA_HACK23_COM_IMPL, null, null)).getValue();
298 			resultSize = resultSize + otherPagesdokumentLista.getDokument().size();
299 			processAll(otherPagesdokumentLista.getDokument(), processStrategy);
300 			LOGGER.info(LOADING_DOCUMENTS, resultSize, dokumentLista.getHits());
301 		}
302 	}
303 
304 	/**
305 	 * Load document list.
306 	 *
307 	 * @param url
308 	 *            the url
309 	 * @param maxNumberPages
310 	 *            the max number pages
311 	 * @return the list
312 	 * @throws XmlAgentException
313 	 *             the xml agent exception
314 	 */
315 	private List<DocumentElement> loadDocumentList(final String url, final int maxNumberPages) throws XmlAgentException {
316 		final List<DocumentElement> result = new ArrayList<>();
317 
318 		DocumentContainerElement dokumentLista = ((JAXBElement<DocumentContainerElement>) xmlAgent.unmarshallXml(
319 				riksdagenDocumentListMarshaller, url, HTTP_DOKUMENTLISTA_RIKSDAGEN_EXTERNAL_MODEL_CIA_HACK23_COM_IMPL,
320 				null, null)).getValue();
321 		result.addAll(dokumentLista.getDokument());
322 		final BigInteger pages = dokumentLista.getTotalPages();
323 		for (int i = 1; i < pages.intValue() && i < maxNumberPages; i++) {
324 			dokumentLista = ((JAXBElement<DocumentContainerElement>) xmlAgent.unmarshallXml(
325 					riksdagenDocumentListMarshaller, fixBrokenUrl(dokumentLista.getNextPage()),
326 					HTTP_DOKUMENTLISTA_RIKSDAGEN_EXTERNAL_MODEL_CIA_HACK23_COM_IMPL, null, null)).getValue();
327 			result.addAll(dokumentLista.getDokument());
328 			LOGGER.info(LOADING_DOCUMENTS, result.size(), dokumentLista.getHits());
329 		}
330 
331 		return result;
332 	}
333 
334 	/* (non-Javadoc)
335 	 * @see com.hack23.cia.service.external.riksdagen.api.RiksdagenDocumentApi#processDocumentList(java.lang.String, java.lang.String, com.hack23.cia.service.external.common.api.ProcessDataStrategy)
336 	 */
337 	@Override
338 	public void processDocumentList(final String changedSinceDate, final String changedToDate,
339 			final ProcessDataStrategy<DocumentElement> processStrategy) throws DataFailureException {
340 		try {
341 			loadAndProcessDocumentList(DOCUMENT_LIST_CHANGED_DATE.replace(CHANGED_SINCE_KEY, changedSinceDate)
342 					.replace(CHANGED_TO_KEY, changedToDate), processStrategy);
343 		} catch (final XmlAgentException e) {
344 			LOGGER.warn(PROBLEM_PROCCESSING_DOCUMENT_BETWEEN_CHANGED_SINCE_DATE_S_AND_CHANGE_TO_DATE, changedSinceDate,
345 					changedToDate);
346 			throw new DataFailureException(e);
347 		}
348 	}
